    <p>Welcome to our platform! To join our team of riders, please ensure you meet the following requirements:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Valid government-issued ID</li>
        <li>Vehicle registration and proof of ownership</li>
        <li>Valid driver's license</li>
        <li>Proof of vehicle insurance</li>
        <li>Pass a background check</li>
        <li>Provide bank account details for receiving payments</li>
        <li>Complete a short training course (optional but recommended)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Revenue Share Model</h2>
    <p>Riders will receive <strong>70-85%</strong> of each ride fare, depending on performance and surge hours. The company retains a service fee of <strong>15-30%</strong>.</p>

    <h2>Ride Allocation</h2>
    <p>Rides are allocated based on proximity, rider ratings, and availability. During peak hours, riders can earn more through surge pricing.</p>

    <h2>Rules & Guidelines</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Maintain professionalism and customer service at all times</li>
        <li>Minimize cancellations to avoid penalties</li>
        <li>Meet minimum ride quotas for continued access to the platform</li>
        <li>Follow company safety and operational guidelines</li>
    </ul>


  
                
